#: ../../../lvgl/docs/intermediate/details/common-widget-features/layouts/grid.rst:139
msgid ""
"The sub-grid is resolved only to a depth of 1 level. That is, a grid can "
"have a sub-grid child, but that sub-grid cannot have another sub-grid."
