#: ../../../lvgl/docs/intermediate/details/common-widget-features/layouts/grid.rst:142
msgid ""
"``LV_GRID_CONTENT`` tracks on the grid are not handled in the sub-grid, "
"only in its own grid."
msgstr "``LV_GRID_CONTENT`` le track sulla grid non vengono gestite nella sub-grid, ma solo nella propria grid."

#: ../../../lvgl/docs/intermediate/details/common-widget-features/layouts/grid.rst:145
msgid ""
"The sub-grid feature works the same as in CSS.  For further information, "
"see `CSS Subgrid`_."
msgstr "La funzionalità della sub-grid funziona come in CSS.  Per ulteriori informazioni, vedere `CSS Subgrid`_."

