#: ../../../lvgl/docs/intermediate/details/integration/bindings/micropython.rst:42
msgid "Why MicroPython + LVGL?"
msgstr "Perché MicroPython + LVGL?"

#: ../../../lvgl/docs/intermediate/details/integration/bindings/micropython.rst:44
msgid ""
"MicroPython `does not have a good native high-level GUI library "
"<https://forum.micropython.org/viewtopic.php?f=18&t=5543>`__. LVGL is an "
"`Object-Oriented Component Based <https://blog.lvgl.io/2018-12-13/extend-"
"lvgl-objects>`__ high-level GUI library, which is a natural candidate to "
