#: ../../../lvgl/docs/intermediate/details/integration/driver/display/ili9341.rst:14
msgid ""
"The ILI9341 LCD controller `driver "
"<https://github.com/lvgl/lvgl/src/drivers/display/ili9341>`__ is a "
