#: ../../../lvgl/docs/intermediate/details/integration/driver/display/st_ltdc.rst:140
msgid ""
"Additionally it is possible to mix layers that have color format on "
":c:macro:`LV_COLOR_FORMAT_ARGB1555` on top of "
":c:macro:`LV_COLOR_FORMAT_RGB565` layers using the DMA2D."
msgstr "Inoltre, è possibile combinare layer con formato colore :c:macro:`LV_COLOR_FORMAT_ARGB1555` sopra i layer :c:macro:`LV_COLOR_FORMAT_RGB565` utilizzando DMA2D."

#: ../../../lvgl/docs/intermediate/details/integration/driver/display/st_ltdc.rst:144
