"Timeline. Note:  this does not preserve its state.  The only way to start"
" it again is to call :cpp:expr:`lv_anim_timeline_start(timeline)`, which "
"starts the Timeline from the beginning or at the point set by "
":cpp:expr:`lv_anim_timeline_set_progress(timeline, progress)`."
