"the whole display image. If two buffers are used, the rendered areas are "
"automatically copied to the other buffer after flushing.  Due to this in "
":ref:`flush_callback` typically only a frame buffer address needs to be "
"changed.  If a button is pressed only the button's area will be redrawn."
