#: ../../../lvgl/docs/intermediate/details/main-modules/display/setup.rst:186
msgid "Flush-Wait Callback"
msgstr "Flush-Wait Callback"

#: ../../../lvgl/docs/intermediate/details/main-modules/display/setup.rst:188
msgid ""
"By using :cpp:func:`lv_display_flush_ready` LVGL will normally spin in a "
"loop while waiting for flushing."
msgstr "By using :cpp:func:`lv_display_flush_ready` LVGL will normally spin in a loop while waiting for flushing."

#: ../../../lvgl/docs/intermediate/details/main-modules/display/setup.rst:191
msgid ""
"However with the help of :cpp:func:`lv_display_set_flush_wait_cb` a "
