#: ../../../lvgl/docs/intermediate/details/main-modules/draw/draw_descriptors.rst:648
msgid ""
"Set ``area``, ``radius``, and ``keep_outside`` parameters. If "
"``keep_outside`` is set to 1, areas outside of ``area`` remain unchanged."
" Otherwise, they are cleared."
msgstr "Set ``area``, ``radius``, and ``keep_outside`` parameters. If ``keep_outside`` is set to 1, areas outside of ``area`` remain unchanged. Otherwise, they are cleared."

#: ../../../lvgl/docs/intermediate/details/main-modules/draw/draw_descriptors.rst:651
msgid "Call :cpp:expr:`lv_draw_mask_rect(layer, &dsc)`."
