#: ../../../lvgl/docs/intermediate/details/main-modules/draw/draw_pipeline.rst:88
msgid ""
"During LVGL's initialization (:cpp:func:`lv_init`), a list of Draw Units "
"is created. If :c:macro:`LV_USE_DRAW_SW` is set to ``1`` in ``lv_conf.h``"
