#: ../../../lvgl/docs/intermediate/details/main-modules/timer.rst:97
msgid ""
"When a Timer is created, its repeat-count is set to ``-1`` to cause it to"
" repeat indefinitely.  You can make a Timer repeat only a given number of"
" times with :cpp:expr:`lv_timer_set_repeat_count(timer, count)`.  By "
"default, once the Timer has run ``count`` times, it will be automatically"
" deleted."
