"background style properties and an arc using the Arc style properties. "
"The Arc's size and position will respect the *padding* style properties."
msgstr ":cpp:enumerator:`LV_PART_MAIN` Draws a background using the typical background style properties and an arc using the Arc style properties. The Arc's size and position will respect the *padding* style properties."

#: ../../../lvgl/docs/intermediate/details/widgets/arc.rst:22
msgid ""
":cpp:enumerator:`LV_PART_INDICATOR` Draws another Arc using the *Arc* "
"style properties. Its padding values are interpreted relative to the "
"background Arc."
