#: ../../../lvgl/docs/intermediate/details/widgets/arc.rst:25
msgid ""
":cpp:enumerator:`LV_PART_KNOB` Draws a handle on the end of the indicator"
" using all background properties and padding values. With zero padding "
"the knob size is the same as the indicator's width. Larger padding makes "
"it larger, smaller padding makes it smaller."
msgstr ":cpp:enumerator:`LV_PART_KNOB` Draws a handle on the end of the indicator using all background properties and padding values. With zero padding the knob size is the same as the indicator's width. Larger padding makes it larger, smaller padding makes it smaller."

