":cpp:expr:`lv_buttonmatrix_set_map(btn_matrix, my_map)`. The declaration "
"of a map should look like ``const char * map[] = {\"button1\", "
"\"button2\", \"button3\", NULL}``. Note that the last element must be "
"either ``NULL`` or an empty string (``\"\"``)!"
