msgstr "update the Label with :cpp:expr:`lv_label_set_text_static(label, buffer)` using that buffer."

#: ../../../lvgl/docs/intermediate/details/widgets/label.rst:75
msgid ""
"Reason:  if you use :cpp:expr:`lv_label_set_text(label, new_text)`, a "
